Package: debconf
Priority: important
Pre-Depends: perl-base (>= 5.6.1-4)
Conflicts: cdebconf, debconf-utils (<< 1.1.0), debconf-tiny (<< 1.0), apt (<< 0.3.12.1), menu (<= 2.1.3-1), dialog (<< 0.9a-20000730-1), whiptail (<< 0.50.17-7)
